title: etnies France welcomes Greg Cuadrado
description:
Greg Cuadrado is a young ripper from Paris. He’s a part of the infamous parisian crew called The Bloby’s.
He’s a super mellow kid that is always down to go skate anything.
If he’s not working at Nozbone skateshop in Paris there’s a strong chance that you will find him cruising the streets from the city with his crew.
